00:18:34,781 --> 00:18:37,482
Troop.

267
00:18:39,619 --> 00:18:40,785
Grenade!

268
00:18:40,787 --> 00:18:42,386
Oh, that's really funny.

269
00:18:42,388 --> 00:18:43,548
Who's the hilarious son of a...

270
00:18:50,296 --> 00:18:51,362
my mistake.

271
00:19:00,507 --> 00:19:01,606
Pack your gear

272
00:19:01,608 --> 00:19:03,708
and be ready to move out
at 1300 hours.

273
00:19:03,710 --> 00:19:06,344
You've been reassigned.

274
00:19:06,346 --> 00:19:08,546
This is
some kind of joke, right?

275
00:19:08,548 --> 00:19:10,781
It's a joke, all right.

276
00:19:10,783 --> 00:19:12,517
You can't reassign me.

277
00:19:12,519 --> 00:19:16,387
Sir, I'm catching the
freedom bird in 7 days.

278
00:19:17,757 --> 00:19:21,425
168 hours.

279
00:19:21,427 --> 00:19:23,861
I'm so short.

280
00:19:23,863 --> 00:19:26,864
I'm so short...
1300 hours, ashford.

281
00:19:31,271 --> 00:19:32,837
¶ Dang me, dang me ¶

